node.text: Going To Miss You Grandad! 🕊You Taught Me So Much, a father figure that I saw everyday growing up in the same house when I was a kid. From teaching me how to change the oil in a car, the tire, jacking it up, cutting the grass, rake leaves, not being lazy, working for everything and knowing you can be anything you want to be if you worked for it. He never said he was tired and if I said I was tired he would say you too young to be saying you tired, that was his mindset and I will take that with me Forever! It’s much more I can say about my grandad he was everything and no one could ever say anything bad about him. He loved everyone he was a real definition of a Man! Love your forever Grandad, May You Rest In Heaven! 🕊😇
